SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY1: Premium users who subscribe will be able to maintain their consolidated health record on the system which summarizes the health issues they have, the treatments they have gone through, details of appointments and emergencies for a given treatment, medication use, family history, diagnostic tests undergone, measurements tracked by him/her regularly relating to health such as blood pressure, blood sugar, calories, sleep etc, vaccinations, health incidents they have been involved in, symptoms they have experienced, blood donations they have made and so on.
SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY2: The premium users and their stakeholders who are authorized can share this record with any person based on an OTP during an emergency or for a second opinion etc with a specific expiry time for giving such access
SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY3: Premium use can maintain a complete health calendar where appointments of doctors, follow up vsits etc can be recorded and reminders triggered on te basis of these dates.
SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY4: Special offers can be made or events organized or content created or forums operated by vendors which are limited to Premium users.
SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY5: Premium users can send adhoc messages to a service provider registered on Paripal with whom the user has a relationship.
SUBSCRIPTION_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY6: All these benefits come to you at a cost of Rs 500 + taxes a year. Go ahead and become a Premium User today.
SPONSORSHIP_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY1: You can become a premium  user by being sponsored by the organization you work for, by a donor (individual/NGO/caregiver institution like a school  or insurance company etc)
SPONSORSHIP_BENEFIT_DETAILS_KEY2: You will then get a message from the sponsor informing you of this and letting you know the subscription package to be chosen by you. Based on this, you can subscribe to become a premium user. This request is subject to authorization by the sponsor before it comes into effect.
